							<item>Hallelúja gleðjist í Drottni <locus from="73r" to="73v">73r-73v</locus></item>
							<item>Kyrie Guð faðir himnaríkis <locus from="73v" to="74r">73v-74r</locus></item>
							<item>Gloria dýrð heiður sé Guði <locus from="74v" to="76r">74v-76r</locus></item>
							<item>Hallelúja Eitt sveinbarn fætt oss <locus from="76v" to="77r">76v-77r</locus></item>
							<item>Vér trúum allir á einn Guð <locus from="77r" to="78v">77r-78v</locus></item>
